<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV34">
<l>ātiyāti yātinīyo raṇṭamāti yātalāṟ</l>
<l>cōtiyāta cōtinīya tuṇmaiyilvi ḷaṅkiṉāy</l>
<l>vētamāki vēḷviyāki viṇṇiṉōṭu maṇṇumā</l>
<l>yātiyāki yāyaṉāya māyameṉṉa māyamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are the [material] cause, the [supporting] cause, the [instrumental] cause!</l>
<l>Because [You] are the cause of the [cosmic] egg, You are the untested flame!</l>
<l rend="indent">That being the truth, You shine!</l>
<l>The wonder of becoming a cowherd, [despite] being the Vedas, the sacrifices,</l>
<l>The earth along with the sky, and the Cause! What an [act of] wonder is [that]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
